trans-unit.source: Represents a configuration element that defines a filter element.
trans-unit.target: 表示組態項目，定義篩選條件的項目。

trans-unit.source: This element is used to define the type of filter, as well as any supporting data or parameters required by the filter.
trans-unit.target: 這個項目用來定義篩選，以及支援資料或篩選所需參數的類型。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the fully-qualified type name of the custom type to be used as a filter.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定要用做為篩選之自訂類型的完整型別名稱。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterType%2A> is set to custom, CustomType is the fully-qualified type name of the class to create.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterType%2A>設定為自訂，CustomType 是要建立之類別的完整限定類型名稱。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterType%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterData%2A> can also contain values to be used during evaluation of the CustomType filter.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterData%2A>也可以包含的 CustomType 篩選評估期間所要使用的值。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterData%2A>

trans-unit.source: The CustomType must implement a constructor that accepts a string value, which contains the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterData%2A> information.
trans-unit.target: CustomType 必須實作接受字串值，其中包含的建構函式<xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterData%2A>資訊。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterData%2A>

trans-unit.source: The fully-qualified type.
trans-unit.target: 完整的類型。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the filter1 data of this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定這個組態項目的 filter1 資料。

trans-unit.source: This value is only used when <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterType*> is set to And.
trans-unit.target: 此值使用的時，才會<xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterType*>設定為 and。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement.FilterType*>

trans-unit.source: The content of Filter1 is only used during evaluation of the AND filter.
trans-unit.target: 在評估 AND 篩選條件，只會用於 Filter1 的內容。

trans-unit.source: The filter1 value of this element.
trans-unit.target: 這個項目的 filter1 值。

trans-unit.source: The content of Filter2 is only used during evaluation of the AND filters.
trans-unit.target: 在評估 AND 篩選時，只會用於 Filter2 內容。
